{"tid":1889534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場直擊] 5星級酒店晚間入住情況","createTime":"2020-02-20T16:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T17:16:05.000Z","uid":68779,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2aaa62ae99e9b3b942c75709029a1ddd2deb089","tid":1889534,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"夜明10點半左右，絕大部住客依個時間都已經係酒店，但又未訓住，所以房內會開燈<br />\n大家數下有幾多間房開左燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGhV9Ty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGhV9Ty.jpg&h=4d9ec0a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNsnPTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNsnPTy.jpg&h=24d0ba2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好以為半島好似好多燈著左好似好多人住<br />\n半島果座低層果一半係office，上半部分黑哂先係酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AL8m5rU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAL8m5rU.jpg&h=6a134e47&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個維港都冇咩遊客，反而幾多香港人跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商場超好行，完全冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nK11, Harbour City, The One, iSquare (雖然iSquare本身都死死下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"2abec37004e323c9a5127bf038bb91ea766ca7c0","tid":1889534,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f545c22d06bb23881d04a17f9baa6bc80